{"tid":488726,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解係香港好似係踩單車最受歧視？","createTime":"2017-12-04T03:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:22:37.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3363a448f4a630cf5cb5636234dfcb7c3def3e2c","tid":488726,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"點解係香港好似係踩單車最受歧視，然後係BB車，最後先到輪椅/電動輪椅？<br />\n我係踩摺車，每次上地鐵前都係入閘前摺好，上車再泊去有d成行/半行都無櫈既位（如下圖），都俾有D口痕阿叔話單車危險又乜又物，應該泊去車頭車尾，摺埋都危險乜乜物物，我心諗車頭車尾就無人喇咩，d電輪椅都幾百磅重，人地行動唔方便需要坐，而上上落落都係要坐係度控制，什至有d人連轉身望後都有困難，向後退既時候睇唔到後，我都只係摺埋捧上地鐵，我危險？我仲要俾傷殘人士歧視返轉頭，岩岩上次係九龍塘火車站月台等lift，前面有兩個人排隊，有個渣手動輪椅既衝埋黎，聲都唔聲攝埋去頭位，夾硬推開我部車過（已摺），唔係我扶住，成部車肯定俾佢推跌&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/115404_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F115404_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f836e5d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d13bbd73f5426aff6b772f099017dfa3737f46e","tid":488726,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><ins>豉油專家(😚)</ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"b7caaed9f2610687cdbe75140d71871f1110ab1a","tid":488726,"uid":1818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"bb車同輪椅都係必須<br />\n比乜鳩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f625f235127e2936d1e207772127008590d6c3","tid":488726,"uid":76728,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"題目： 點解<span style=\"color: red;\">喺</span>香港<span style=\"color: red;\">帶單車搭地鐵</span>最受歧視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真答：<br />\n1. 架車摺埋咗都係大大件件、岩岩巉巉，無論碰撞面積定係危險度都係最高。<br />\n2. 單車唔係必需品。<br />\n<br />\n真正原因：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成車人搭地鐵，9成朝早唔係趕返工就係捱完夜更收工，見到你條仆街咁有閒情咁有精力踩單車..... 呵呵....."},{"pid":"d2ba4760edfb23b05f548fd496220935a01c486b","tid":488726,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"有次個fd 推單車入lift 落月台<br />\n之後有個阿叔講：有手有腳踩乜鬼單車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b195fa342feddad54ee1cbbd8618077982e33915","tid":488726,"uid":7854,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:29:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母踩單車喎咁撚健康咁撚威<br />\n喎<br />\n仲搭咩地鐵?<br />\n<br />\n同開住冷氣講環保有乜分別? 踩番屋企啦豬閪</span>"},{"pid":"026fe322a105d678e28d689b6c9c06c013bc4fae","tid":488726,"uid":132557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"樓主最錯係係連登問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d1c467e755ada75532351c60184454c7946fd","tid":488726,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><ins>豉油專家(😚)</ins></span></span></blockquote><br />\n咪放我上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fc91d1e98dd4a0e29e9a996539edc61cac854b","tid":488726,"uid":61463,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母踩單車喎咁撚健康咁撚威<br />\n喎<br />\n仲搭咩地鐵?<br />\n<br />\n同開住冷氣講環保有乜分別? 踩番屋企啦豬閪</span></blockquote><br />\n想睇ching示範踩單車過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9c274224216397b02f9fc6df75b8246b44ae45","tid":488726,"uid":97136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"講真 